{"tid":1614312,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[GTA攻略：天道師] 其實執行天道既時候可以做多少少野黎昇華整個行動（主要做比外界睇）","createTime":"2019-10-02T17:51:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T12:01:53.000Z","uid":34241,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2f6dd467f6cffd7a9e1a8940a7257bc75f26e37d","tid":1614312,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:51:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>ＧＴＡ　ＯＮＬＩＮＥ最新攻略：</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">１：當場宣讀罪狀</span></span><br />\n好多路人冇追得咁貼，<br />\n唔知點解某一間成日幫襯既鋪頭會遭天譴，<br />\n事後文宣解釋係好花工夫，文宣流傳需要時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n時間遲左　觀感會差好多，<br />\n而且事後各人意見有機會不一致<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n（連登都係咁，更何況公海）<br />\n亦都未必兜得返哂，<br />\n所以<span style=\"color: red;\">開波既時候就要解釋</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n開波前大聲宣讀罪狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，點解要懲罰佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n（又可以用黎疏散入面既人）<br />\n開緊波繼續用大聲公講，<br />\n講比周圍既人知，講埋比睇緊直播既人知<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">２：拉ＢＡＮＮＥＲ／噴字（講原因，針對黨媒）</span></span><br />\n黨媒＋敵方文宣一定會ＣＵＴ頭ＣＵＴ尾，偽造事實<br />\n甚至ＭＵＴＥ／用旁白蓋過宣言，<br />\n所以全程都要用<span style=\"color: red;\">靜態背景</span>黎助攻，<br />\n例如Selfie Bomb拉ＢＡＮＮＥＲ（參考<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">是是旦旦</span></strong>，黨媒驚到ＦＩＮＧ鏡頭／轉返主台），<br />\n對家想播到精華出街就冇得ＣＵＴ，<br />\n焗住影埋ＢＡＮＮＥＲ出街，咁就有另類宣傳作用，<br />\n黨媒一係完全唔播，一播就幫你宣傳埋，簡直易過宣傳易<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢敢落ＩＣＯＮ／ＥＦＦＥＣＴ／打格就比人知佢掩蓋事實<br />\n暗藍媒體有機會露底<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">３：留低警告字眼</span></span><br />\n睇戲做得多，「欠債還錢」「血債血償」「Ｘ債Ｘ還」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。。。<br />\n人地通常會留低有威嚇性、警告既字眼，寫低要求，甚至會預告行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n但記得唔好淨係留「光復香港」「時代革命」「五大訴求」呢Ｄ短句，<br />\n太行貨，解釋唔到點解係呢一間而唔係隔離果間<br />\n甚至留「黑警」「黑社會」「暴政」呢Ｄ唔係直接關果間野事<br />\n要留就留「ＸＸＸＸ出賣港人」「泯滅良心／人性」「替天行道」「死不足惜」「驅逐中資」「天譴」「殺人兇手」「與港人為敵」「恥與為伍」呢Ｄ字句，針對性強好多<br />\n亦都係寫比其他敵對商戶睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>你ＸＸＸＸ，下個到你</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">４：幫手放大、宣傳佢既取態</span></span><br />\n文字可能都係空泛左ｄ，始終唔夠強力<br />\n可以考慮快速建立連儂牆，<br />\n留返一幅牆貼文宣，<br />\nｐｒｉｎｔ哂佢ｄ豐功偉論出黎（ｆｂ／ｉｇ／ｗｈａｔｓａｐｐ　ｃａｐ圖），<br />\n傳媒可以直接影直接出街，做少份資料搜集，ｗｏｒｋｌｏａｄ又輕鬆ｄ<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n路人事後又可以留低睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甚至搵手足派下傳單比現場都仲得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n撐犬：貼「殺人兇手」、「幫兇」、「填命」。。。<br />\n護旗手：赤ｎａｚｉ<br />\n撐蝗：唔使教啦，大把料可以貼<br />\n<br />\n注意：<br />\n未來行動會愈趨困難<br />\n注意以上動作會耗費幾多時間<br />\n不宜過於執著，達到目標／危險迫近就即散<br />\n始終替天行道最講究<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>風林火山</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>「故其疾如風，<br />\n其徐如林，<br />\n侵掠如火，<br />\n不動如山，<br />\n難知如陰，<br />\n動如雷震。」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n祝：早日１００％通關　<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb1e447f2f3e41fb22ff776f20108407bae21426","tid":1614312,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b3592187a2d48b843d317688362983c93e85b9","tid":1614312,"uid":303052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RZ1GPbN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRZ1GPbN.jpg&h=2767630d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d8qo2wQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd8qo2wQ.gif&h=e9ecabc4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6eda074ad8990ebb666296eb168334fd421019f","tid":1614312,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T19:15:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4317e691d0ff5e0a678d2bbfdb524acdeafc74","tid":1614312,"uid":218131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T19:17:05.000Z","msg":"深夜一推"},{"pid":"f5be3aa7ea2fa36c7a6b72ccb94401656bdbe01b","tid":1614312,"uid":309002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T19:17:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">啱啱喺大圍發生，防暴警察強行除記者面罩及打市民，請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">防暴除記者豬嘴！！！</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/3172730676101308?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkon9agroup%2Fpermalink%2F3172730676101308%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7DbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=e8001fbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/3172730676101308?sfns=mo</a></span>"},{"pid":"9c1a391c8dad8ca4106f3d8b2284fc2fe55c440c","tid":1614312,"uid":164517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T19:21:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f5daeb2c67b11a20a897b3060a89eb62bc483cb","tid":1614312,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T23:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"269f4a646fb4e4e125ed7258689e7e9dc660c09a","tid":1614312,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T00:49:46.000Z","msg":"冇人睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa97337942ace0ef9c169897cee3423bdcc5993d","tid":1614312,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:22:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0cb3861823af293faacb005fe8cb6a07b6ff14cc","tid":1614312,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:23:41.000Z","msg":"前線手足求你入嚟花3秒睇睇，可以改變全場革命<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1614758\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1614758</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e8e80721aca2b566ce0b0071e17ee66ca4c7568a","tid":1614312,"uid":121409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:38:31.000Z","msg":"支持新興職業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但腦入面個職業形象唔知點解係陳雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da9d34f0fe5d237716768b0fd87a5e7c8c96574","tid":1614312,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c80864e28e5cca655f4054a4be3a07b04a645a91","tid":1614312,"uid":45486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:22:37.000Z","msg":"民間制裁分級制度<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1615054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1615054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ab4ac679c3f71e6f6d2141e0b7619333781caa5f","tid":1614312,"uid":31111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:23:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894fbabd1e0d91e51545b833b2d2649a8df0c06c","tid":1614312,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e8b3d0e4f1b9eff1ca14378ded341be80256a0e","tid":1614312,"uid":237425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:55:23.000Z","msg":"宣布罪行，行動正名合義化<br />\n有用<br />\n你話佢係黑社會虐打市民<br />\n大家自然唔撚可憐佢"},{"pid":"3368b80fb80727f85b524da9d0baa6b444e73774","tid":1614312,"uid":275750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:01:53.000Z","msg":"早日通關<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}